v2.5.1
  * Update Symfony to 2.8.1
  * configure travis-ci service

v2.5.0
  * Update Symfony to 2.8.1
  * Better role management
    * ROLE_DONATION_EDITOR : Can edit customer details (will later be able to add/edit intent)
  * Integration tests with behat
  * Update phing tasks

v2.4.7
  * install behat
  * better role hierarchy
    * ROLE_SUPER_ADMIN : all powers,
    * ROLE_ADMIN : manager user accounts
    * ROLE_CMS : Manage blocks, layouts and affectations,
    * ROLE_AFFECTATION : Manage affectations
    * ROLE_USER : Acces dashboard, customer and intent details

v2.4.6
  * Update to Symfony 2.7.7
  * Remove any deprecation warning in application code
  * Add a title to any tunnel Amount box in front office (Donate once / Donate each month)


v2.4.5
   * use better suited fonts,
   * fix amount styles
   * fix styles of buttons


